Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DECIMAL value: 'AUX_LOB_META'
Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DECIMAL value: 'AUX_LOB_PIECE'
Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DECIMAL value: 'INDEX'
